/02/21/star-wars-battlefront-classic-collection-ps4-ps5-features-reveal/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方公告</a>中写道。</p><p>玩家还可以“加入精英冲锋队第 501 军团，在《星球大战：前线 2》的战役模式中体验达斯·维达的崛起。”</p><p>这一消息是与<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/nintendo">任天堂</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/how-to-watch-the-nintendo-direct-today-2-3590676">今年首个直接展示会</a>同时发布的。</p><p>除了宣布<em>《星球大战：前线：经典合集》</em>之外，任天堂还确认了两款<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/xbox-game-studios">Xbox 游戏工作室的</a>游戏将登陆 Nintendo Switch。 <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/grounded">《Grounded》</a></em>将于 4 月 16 日发行， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/pentiment">《Pentiment》</a></em>将于明天 2 月 22 日<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xbox-game-studios-grounded-and-pentiment-confirm-nintendo-switch-release-3590800">发行。这是这两款游戏首次在“竞争对手”游戏机上推出。</a></p><p>其他消息是，期待已久的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/elden-ring">《Elden Tree》</a></em>扩展包终于有了发布日期。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/elden-ring-share-first-look-at-the-shadow-of-the-erdtree-expansion-3590766">《The <em>Shadow Of The Erdtree》</em>将于 6 月 21 日发布</a>，并引入新的地图和叙事，以及新的武器、魔法和敌人。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/original-star-wars-battlefront-games-being-rereleased-in-new-classic-collection-3590829">原创《星球大战：前线》游戏在新的“经典合集”中重新发布，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
老鹰乐队《加州旅馆》手写歌词被盗，审判开始https://www.nme.com/news/music/Trial-begins-over-stolen-handwriting-lyrics-to-the-eagles-hotel-california-3590794?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=Trial-begins-over-加州老鹰酒店的手写歌词被盗Tom SkinnerWed, 21 Feb 2024 15:23:48 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3590794 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheEagles-performing-live-on-stage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="老鹰乐队现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheEagles-performing-live-on-stage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheEagles-performing-live-on-stage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheEagles-performing-live-on-stage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheEagles-performing-live-on-stage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheEagles-performing-live-on-stage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheEagles-performing-live-on-stage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>唐·亨利预计将被传唤为明星证人</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/trial-begins-over-stolen-handwritten-lyrics-to-the-eagles-hotel-california-3590794">因老鹰乐队《加州旅馆》手写歌词被盗而引发的后审判</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheEagles-performing-live-on-stage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="老鹰乐队现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheEagles-performing-live-on-stage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheEagles-performing-live-on-stage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheEagles-performing-live-on-stage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheEagles-performing-live-on-stage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheEagles-performing-live-on-stage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/TheEagles-performing-live-on-stage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>涉及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-eagles">老鹰乐队</a>经典歌曲《加州旅馆》手写歌词的审判已在纽约开始，定于今天（2 月 21 日星期三）听取开庭陈词。</p><p>早在 2022 年，格伦·霍洛维茨、爱德华·科辛斯基和摇滚名人堂馆长克雷格·因西亚迪就被指控试图出售 1977 年单曲及其后续歌曲《Life In The Fast Lane》中的手写音符和歌词。</p><p>当时的官​​员估计，这些由 Eagles 联合创始人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/don-henley">Don Henley</a>撰写的文件总价值超过 100 万美元（792,000 英镑）。这些作品于 20 世纪 70 年代被盗，亨利多年来一直试图找回它们。</p><p>据称，它们于 2005 年被典当给了珍本书籍经销商霍洛维茨 (Horowitz)。霍洛维茨、因恰尔迪 (Inciardi) 和纪念品销售商科辛斯基 (Kosinski) 随后开始向多家拍卖行出售，并试图强迫亨利买回它们。</p><p>据<a href="https://apnews.com/article/hotel-california-lyrics-manuscript-trial-eagles-henley-8ec3a28657365ecce6bfd4003ead494a" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>美联社报道</em></a>，这三人均对共谋罪和其他多项指控表示不认罪。他们的律师声称，此案“指控了根本不存在的犯罪行为，不公平地玷污了受人尊敬的专业人士的声誉”。 </p><div class="ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0" data-component="text-block"><div class="ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1"><p>审判开始后，曼哈顿地区检察官办公室预计将传唤亨利作为明星证人。检察官需要证明文件被盗。 </p><div class="ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0" data-component="text-block"><div class="ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1"><p>据说，当作家埃德·桑德斯在 70 年代末开始为老鹰乐队撰写传记时，老鹰乐队允许他访问他们的档案。后来，他于 2005 年以 50,000 美元（39,609 英镑）的价格将笔记本卖给了 Horowitz 先生。</p><p>亨利声称他从未向桑德斯提供过歌词，桑德斯也没有因此案受到指控。然而，辩护律师却提出了相反的建议，并对亨利对事件的说法提出了质疑。</p><p> “我们相信亨利先生自愿向桑德斯先生提供歌词，”律师斯科特·埃德尔曼上周在法庭上表示。 </p><figure id="attachment_3268167" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3268167" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3268167" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/TheEagles_2022_1.jpg" alt="老鹰" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/TheEagles_2022_1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/TheEagles_2022_1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/TheEagles_2022_1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/TheEagles_2022_1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/TheEagles_2022_1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/TheEagles_2022_1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3268167" class="wp-caption-text">老鹰。图片来源：Roberto Ricciuti/Redferns </figcaption></figure><div class="Page-storyBody gtmMainScrollContent"><div class="RichTextStoryBody RichTextBody"><p>被告决定放弃陪审团，由柯蒂斯·法伯法官来决定判决。</p></div></div><p> 2022 年受到指控后，因西亚迪在摇滚名人堂的职务被暂停。</p><p>在当时的一份声明中（通过<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/eagles-hotel-california-lyrics-charged-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-1381952/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《滚石》</em></a>杂志），老鹰乐队经理欧文·阿佐夫表示：“这一行动揭露了音乐纪念品销售的真相，这些纪念品隐藏在合法性的外表之下，是高度私人的、被盗的物品。</p><p> “任何人都无权出售非法获得的财产或从公然盗窃不可替代的音乐史作品中获利。这些手写歌词是 Don Henley 在他 50 多年的职业生涯中创造的遗产的一个组成部分。”</p><p>上个月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eagles-add-two-extra-final-uk-shows-to-the-long-goodbye-manchester-farewell-residency-3577094">，老鹰乐队宣布在曼彻斯特告别驻场演出“漫长的告别”之前额外举行两场英国决赛</a>。您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/eagles-tickets/artist/734977?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=XgW0xiTitxyPTxFx-k0T327XUkHzhSy9nThh3Y0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到任何剩余的门票。</p></div></div></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/trial-begins-over-stolen-handwritten-lyrics-to-the-eagles-hotel-california-3590794">因老鹰乐队《加州旅馆》手写歌词被盗而引发的后审判</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
